SAAS=software as a service
PAAS=platform as a service
IAAS=infrastructure as a service
CAPEX=capital expenditure
OPEX=operational expenditure
High Availability=your ability to ensure that a service remains available
Scalability=your ability to grow rapidly or unimpeded
Vertical Scaling=scaling Up
Horizontal Scaling=scaling Out
Elasticity=your ability to automatically shrink and grow to meet demand
High Durability=your ability to recover from a disaster
Fault Tolerance=your ability to prevent failure
Disaster Recovery=your ability to recover from a failure
Geo Distribution=your ability to deploy apps and data to regional datacenters around the globe
